  "texts": [
    "Shedding light on attractive but sub-optimal projects can skew exploration in a sub-optimal direction and deprive agents and society of breakthrough innovations.",
    "We use the GABE framework (powered by OpenAI's GPT-4 model) to extend the Hoelzemann et al. (2024) theory by simulating this same experiment with AI agents.",
    "As we will describe in detail, we develop a central experimental engine that feeds multiple AI agents the objectives and rules of the game and coordinates their actions under different experimental conditions.",
    "We first use this method to replicate the conditions of the original experiment and reproduce the results derived from human subjects.",
    "Our analysis shows that we are able to do so with a remarkable degree of accuracy."
